Title.........DeLEGiONS Folder lister

         Company.......DeLEGiON

         Release.Date..1/10/2008

         Disc[s].......N/A 

         Protection....None

         type..........Tool

         Size..........63.7kbs

         Url...........N/A

         Language......Any
         


         DESCRIPTION
         ~~~~~~~~~~~
         This is a little exe file that if you copy it into a folder
         or in the root of a drive it will make a txt file called List.txt
         you will be able to read all the folders in that directory in this
         file.This comes in handy for folks who want to organize or to list
         there uploads etc on a site.We find this tool very handy.

         
         System Requirements
         ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
         DOS


         Installation
         ~~~~~~~~~~~~
       1.Unrar and use
